This paper is about deep reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper proposes a new exploration strategy based on intrinsic motivation, which is a common topic in reinforcement learning research. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also applies the proposed method to continuous control tasks and games in the Atari RAM domain, which suggests that it may be relevant to sub-categories such as cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
